Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.68,0:02:50.40,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,COURTROOM CONFRONTATION II: KISAKI VS KUJOU\N(PART TWO)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:54.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for your assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.44,0:02:56.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.32,0:02:58.61,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Did you find anything that'll help you in the trial?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.32,0:02:58.65,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Arima Masahiko (35)\NProprietor of an Italian Restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.86,0:03:03.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, since the police and the prosecution have already investigated everything thoroughly...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.95,0:03:08.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not like we could have found out anything new.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:08.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.54,0:03:10.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:14.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about having dinner at my restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.21,0:03:17.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll bring out my best wine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.59,0:03:19.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.09,0:03:22.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since he's offering, let's give it a try!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.93,0:03:23.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.47,0:03:26.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't Ran waiting at home?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:28.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.44,0:03:32.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, she is welcome as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:34.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry to trouble you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:35.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:38.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Meals taste better when eaten as a group, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:41.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then we shall accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:55.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This wine is quite magnificent!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:57.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm honored that you find it to your liking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:03:59.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The atmosphere of your restaurant is also lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.47,0:04:01.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.76,0:04:06.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've also been called to appear in the next hearing as a witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.80,0:04:09.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please go easy on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:14.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believe you discovered your father when you went to deliver something he left behind, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.81,0:04:18.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He had left his glasses behind after having taken his meal here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.23,0:04:19.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.32,0:04:20.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Reading glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:24.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, please take your time and enjoy your meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:34.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somehow, the pasta doesn't seem quite up to the standards of a fine restaurant, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:36.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seems so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.21,0:04:38.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a little too much olive oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:43.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, how is it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.72,0:04:45.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you thought up a strategy for the next hearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.76,0:04:47.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's pretty difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:51.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's impossible unless you change the legal system.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:53.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.73,0:04:56.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's impossible to overturn it from being a robbery-murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.98,0:04:59.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His daughter can already confirm that, because of his feelings as a parent...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.82,0:05:03.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He had a reason to hold a grudge towards the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.40,0:05:07.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you're saying to confirm the prosecution's version of events...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.03,0:05:09.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And try for a lesser sentence due to the extenuating circumstances?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:11.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's probably no other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.41,0:05:12.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This isn't a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:15.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The defendant says that he had no intention to murder the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:18.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll get trounced by the Madonna exactly because you're still being taken in by that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:22.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't remember you ever having gone into a courtroom battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.21,0:05:25.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know why I ever wanted to help you in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.47,0:05:29.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, stop it you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.64,0:05:31.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did we come to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.93,0:05:34.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I remember correctly, in the list of articles left at the scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.35,0:05:40.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It should be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.94,0:05:43.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.44,0:05:45.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The decisive evidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.53,0:05:47.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.41,0:05:49.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.62,0:05:51.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looking at the court documents...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.16,0:05:54.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was just something that bothered me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.41,0:05:55.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something that bothered you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.08,0:05:59.79,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,List of Articles Found at the Crime Scene\N1. Glass Ashtray\N2. 1 Pair of Army Cotton Gloves\N3. Eyeglasses screw\N4. Golf Ball
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.08,0:05:59.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, in this list of articles left at the scene of the crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:05:59.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.38,0:06:03.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once again you're going through important documents without permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.80,0:06:06.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:11.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're going to be like that, you'd better come up with something to help Mom out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.18,0:06:17.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't even care if that stubborn woman gets beaten to a pulp by the Madonna!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.60,0:06:21.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're saying that, but you really don't have any confidence you can win against that Madonna, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.94,0:06:23.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.19,0:06:25.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That kind of little girl, I could take on two of them at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.57,0:06:27.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, how about if you become the defense attorney, Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:29.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.41,0:06:31.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad doesn't have the qualifications to become a defense attorney.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:34.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if he were to become a special counsel, it'd be all right, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:36.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:39.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a policy in which, as long as it is at the request of the defendant...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.67,0:06:44.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,h person who only possesses ordinary qualifications can represent them in court.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.67,0:06:50.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let the people at the court hear one of your great deductions, Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.68,0:06:53.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of my great deductions, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:57.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter how hard the case, in my hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.81,0:07:03.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's insisted upon, I guess I'd think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.23,0:07:09.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That person is going to become a special counsel?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:10.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.32,0:07:12.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said that he absolutely wants to be of assistance to you, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:16.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks, but no thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.16,0:07:17.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.12,0:07:19.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's so rare that Dad gets this kind of idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:24.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even so, I can't think of any way that person could be helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.67,0:07:25.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.80,0:07:33.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have a message from Uncle, for Kisaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} to go to the crime scene tonight, with the building manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.18,0:07:35.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To that building?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:40.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said you'd be able to see something that would influence the direction of the trial!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.73,0:07:42.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The direction of the trial?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.81,0:07:46.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry for all the trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.57,0:07:48.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't really mind, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.65,0:07:50.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just what do you want with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.70,0:07:53.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, even I don't know exactly...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.70,0:07:57.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Building Manager...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:08:00.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you once again do what you did on the night of the incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.04,0:08:02.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.33,0:08:04.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is our man?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.92,0:08:07.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's just outside, making preparations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:11.13,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Got it, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.09,0:08:12.38,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Akiyama Takuya (56) Building Manager
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:12.38,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Do the same thing again, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:17.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me see, on that night we came into this office and no one was here, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.85,0:08:21.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Arima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} peeked into the company president's office through this small window...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:23.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And said, "There's someone there," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.98,0:08:25.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.15,0:08:27.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then when I peeked in...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:29.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:32.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:33.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:35.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is someone inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.41,0:08:36.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:39.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kisaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}, why don't you confirm it with your own eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:43.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:46.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I recreated the trick like Uncle told me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.25,0:08:48.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Trick?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.25,0:08:50.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, could it be that the culprit is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.42,0:08:55.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle said he'd explain everything in detail at the trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:09:00.97,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The Case of the Robbery-Murder of the Real Estate Company President\NSecond Public Hearing
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:10.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If Mom and Dad are joining hands, there's nothing to fear, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:14.78,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Inoue Takashi (55)\NSuspect
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.99,0:09:13.57,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.78,0:09:17.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never would have expected her to request for Mouri Kogorou as special counsel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.74,0:09:20.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Counselor Kisaki must be at a total loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.12,0:09:22.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All rise!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:38.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akiyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.34,0:09:43.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're testifying that you saw, from the small window in the door to the company president's office...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.35,0:09:45.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim was being beaten by the culprit, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.35,0:09:47.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.02,0:09:49.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How many times did the culprit hit the victim?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:53.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From what I saw, it was three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:55.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And right after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.86,0:09:58.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You heard the sound of the victim falling to the floor, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:01.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No further questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.53,0:10:03.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Counsel, you may proceed with the cross-examination.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.63,0:10:10.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akiyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.13,0:10:14.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About your witnessing of the victim being struck...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.67,0:10:17.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you see the face of the person doing the striking?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.68,0:10:23.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't see the person doing the striking directly...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.18,0:10:28.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you didn't see the person directly, what did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.81,0:10:33.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit's shadow reflected on the wall from the light outside the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.36,0:10:37.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.70,0:10:42.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What you saw was only the culprit's shadow, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:43.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.62,0:10:45.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.04,0:10:48.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if it was his shadow, as long as.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:51.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,hen, I'll ask you one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.71,0:10:58.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akiyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, was the defendant here the culprit that you saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.34,0:11:04.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, the only thing I saw was the shadow of the person doing the striking, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.43,0:11:08.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you don't know whether the person doing the striking was the defendant or not, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.64,0:11:10.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.81,0:11:14.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No further questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:18.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is Dad doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.57,0:11:20.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's been sleeping the whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:22.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His performance is up next, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.82,0:11:24.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.37,0:11:28.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moving on, we call witness Arima to the stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.91,0:11:30.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Arima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.08,0:11:35.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Along with the building manager, you heard the sound of the victim falling, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.79,0:11:36.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.55,0:11:37.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.21,0:11:43.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then you rammed in the president's locked office door, and plunged into the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:45.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:47.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was after the culprit had already fled through the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.81,0:11:51.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My father—I mean President Ootsu—was on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.39,0:11:54.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was the condition of the safe at that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.90,0:11:56.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was left open.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.57,0:11:58.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No further questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.94,0:12:00.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go ahead, Counsel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.07,0:12:08.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, I guess it's about time for me to overturn this trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.66,0:12:10.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad, do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:15.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, we'll take a look at Uncle's skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:35.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, special counsel, please begin your questioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.23,0:12:36.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.19,0:12:46.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You went to Ootsu Real Estate at about 9:00 at night in order to deliver something the victim left behind, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.37,0:12:47.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.07,0:12:49.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to deliver the reading glasses that my father left behind in my shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.08,0:12:53.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, the door to the office was locked, and you couldn't go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.91,0:12:55.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.83,0:12:59.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But really, the door wasn't locked, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.17,0:13:04.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the victim was in the company president's office, checking the money in the safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:07.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.97,0:13:09.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't mean that I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.68,0:13:14.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, just that you also had the chance to commit the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:16.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.10,0:13:17.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would I do that to my father-in-law?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.36,0:13:22.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When money is involved, even direct parent-child relationships are pushed to the side.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.69,0:13:27.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Surprisingly, Uncle has struck a good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.12,0:13:32.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The question is obviously nothing more than conjecture!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.37,0:13:33.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Objection sustained.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.25,0:13:38.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the defense could please develop their argument on the basis of clearly defined evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.83,0:13:39.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.75,0:13:46.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From my seven years of experience, it happens very often that the first person to discover the body is the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.18,0:13:49.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, using your seven years of experience...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.30,0:13:53.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How would you explain the articles left at the scene of the crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:57.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the defendant's fingerprints on the dial of the safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.52,0:14:02.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the witness and the victim were arguing over the money...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:04.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The defendant took in the situation from outside the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:08.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is again unestablished.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.78,0:14:13.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And further, after the witness beat the victim down and left...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:18.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The defendant snuck in and went to steal the money in the safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.63,0:14:23.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, then who was this culprit the building manager witnessed?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.30,0:14:27.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In actuality, the victim was not yet dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.88,0:14:31.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And so he regained consciousness, got into a struggle with the defendant...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:39.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, then as we were saying, the one who murdered the victim was the defendant, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:42.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess that's what it comes down to, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.15,0:14:44.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:47.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you here for the sake of defending the defendant?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.24,0:14:52.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am here as a Great Detective in order to shed light on the truth of this case!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:54.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was a fool to rely on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:14:57.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.04,0:14:58.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:14:59.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.16,0:15:01.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm still in the middle of this important...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.54,0:15:04.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would be appreciated if the marital spat could be conducted elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.76,0:15:09.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad sucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:13.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess that's about as far as Uncle can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.85,0:15:17.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, just sit down and shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.77,0:15:18.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What am I, an ornament?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.44,0:15:24.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I retract my previous statements.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.77,0:15:25.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your Honor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.32,0:15:27.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's enough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.73,0:15:34.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The defendant snuck into that room before Arima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} entered, not afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.49,0:15:39.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, as he was about to open the safe, he was discovered by the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:43.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Without thinking, he struck the victim down and immediately fled.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:46.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The problem is with what happened after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.75,0:15:54.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The defendant was convinced that he accidentally killed the victim, but in actuality the victim only lost consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:15:59.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And immediately after that, the victim was murdered by someone who came to the scene of the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.98,0:16:01.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you saying that's me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.60,0:16:06.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You testified the victim forgot his reading glasses at your shop, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.44,0:16:12.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does he need his reading glasses even while he's eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.07,0:16:14.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Without them, he can't even read the menu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.28,0:16:17.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:22.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the indictment, it is written that the victim was forced by the culprit to open the safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.62,0:16:24.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he didn't have his reading glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.79,0:16:28.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder how the victim turned the dials on the safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.38,0:16:34.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that dark office in which only the neon signs from the neighboring building were shining.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.76,0:16:35.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.59,0:16:37.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have no idea either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.89,0:16:42.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wasn't the victim still alive up until you delivered the reading glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:45.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.77,0:16:49.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.02,0:16:50.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have a wound on your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.07,0:16:51.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Leave it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.99,0:16:53.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.65,0:16:55.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was after he had discovered the robber.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.57,0:16:59.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After he regained consciousness, what he should have been the most concerned about was the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.12,0:17:01.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're looking for your glasses, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.88,0:17:09.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you saw that money...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.46,0:17:12.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A murderous urge was born within you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.88,0:17:17.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you murdered the victim with the toppled ashtray.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:20.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prosecutor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.18,0:17:24.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was called here as a witness, but now I'm being treated as the culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.94,0:17:26.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.19,0:17:28.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have forgotten one important fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.27,0:17:32.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That the witness has an alibi for the time of the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.40,0:17:33.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.40,0:17:35.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During the time when my father was being struck down and fell...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:37.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was on the outside of the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.66,0:17:39.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Along with the building manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.08,0:17:43.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You probably didn't hear the building manager's testimony.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.08,0:17:47.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He is saying that he didn't see the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.75,0:17:48.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:50.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The shadow of the assailant...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.38,0:17:52.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The shadow reflected on the wall, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:56.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After you committed the crime for the sake of money...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.51,0:17:59.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You desperately tried to think of a way to make it seem as if it were the result of a robbery.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.80,0:18:01.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's when a certain mechanism came to mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.18,0:18:09.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A mechanism using a clock in the president's office that had a decoration attached.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.77,0:18:12.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your Honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.03,0:18:18.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a clock in the same shape as the one in the company president's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.20,0:18:23.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We believe that the culprit probably set this clock to ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.83,0:18:27.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And set the doll up so that its movement was reflected on the wall using the light from the window...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.46,0:18:33.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An optical illusion that lead the building manager to misunderstand the time of the murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.80,0:18:35.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.05,0:18:36.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about the sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.55,0:18:39.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The building manager and I, we heard the sound of my father collapsing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.01,0:18:42.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a simple trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.72,0:18:46.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You most likely took a golf ball with a string attached to it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.22,0:18:49.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And put it under the leg of a desk in the company president's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.06,0:18:53.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Having prepared the end of the string to stick out under the door...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.86,0:18:57.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You pulled the string as the building manager was peering in the small window and being taken by surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.74,0:19:04.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How's that for a pretty simple trick?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.79,0:19:09.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have any proof?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:11.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That kind of trick...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.04,0:19:12.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyone could have done it, couldn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:15.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Show me evidence that I was the one to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.50,0:19:17.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly as the witness said!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.21,0:19:20.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're going to go as far as to claim that, I would like to see evidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.26,0:19:22.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As far as evidence, Prosecutor Kujou...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.47,0:19:26.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's in the list of articles recovered from the crime scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.39,0:19:28.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the list?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.35,0:19:33.90,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,List of Articles Found at the Crime Scene\N1. Glass Ashtray\N2. 1 Pair of Army Cotton Gloves\N3. Eyeglasses screw\N4. Golf Ball
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:33.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's an eyeglasses screw in that list, isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.40,0:19:40.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's from the victim's reading glasses, I wonder when it fell there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.07,0:19:43.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He should have left his reading glasses at the restaurant, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.28,0:19:53.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no other way to think of it except that it came off when the victim was struck down by the culprit, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.04,0:19:56.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, Arima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.80,0:20:01.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You used your work apron to wipe the fingerprints off the ashtray, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.80,0:20:08.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to the forensic examination of the ashtray, the fingerprints had been wiped down by an oily cloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.02,0:20:18.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I request a complete analysis comparison of the oil on the ashtray against the olive oil used in Arima's restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.36,0:20:23.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Arima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.57,0:20:28.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After the incident, you repaid a debt of 5,000,000 yen to a money lending company, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.37,0:20:35.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can recover that money, and examine the fingerprints from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.80,0:20:41.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad deserved it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.42,0:20:43.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That abusive man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.05,0:20:48.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's great, isn't it, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.76,0:20:49.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That the money was untouched...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.93,0:20:52.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you want this money?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:53.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But look here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.23,0:20:57.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't return the money I lent you by next week...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.40,0:21:01.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll evict you from that shop, even if you are my adopted son-in-law!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.74,0:21:06.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's as Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} said.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.03,0:21:07.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one who killed my father was me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.37,0:21:16.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your Honor!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.71,0:21:21.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We revise the indictment against Defendant Inoue from Robbery-Murder to Attempted Robbery...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.59,0:21:25.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And additionally would like to prepare an accusation against suspect Arima.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.34,0:21:28.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How does that sit with the defense?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.18,0:21:30.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is appropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.60,0:21:34.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, we conclude the trial for this matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.65,0:23:05.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kisaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.69,0:23:09.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For helping me realize the error of my conclusion...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.65,0:23:11.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.49,0:23:14.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was merely carrying out my duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.83,0:23:17.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, see you at the next trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.83,0:23:25.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, in celebration of the conclusion of the trial, why don't we all go out to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.00,0:23:27.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, I am hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.30,0:23:31.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Delicious wine and Italian food, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.13,0:23:33.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should go with sake and fresh sashimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.97,0:23:34.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.85,0:23:38.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cold beer and tempura so hot you'd have to blow at it while you eat it—that'd be great!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.22,0:23:41.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or even Chinese food and old Chinese wine...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.02,0:23:43.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will he ever come to a decision?
